Class Account

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.allisonrodenbaugh.springboothelloworld.Account
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CheckingAccount, SavingsAccount

    public abstract class Account
extends java.lang.Object

    Functionality for Account

    The Account class implements the functionality for manipulating account data

    Note: This class does implements the Template Method to perform withdrawals for the different Account types depicted in it's subclasses.

    Since:
    Fall 2018
